                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 337.11/286</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-03-14">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 14, 1917</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your 13th. Heavy losses at Francisco occurred two weeks ago. Cuban troops now
                    there.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gonzales</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
